{"tid":2399464,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Donki拿走「飛機杯」自己用　食環署職員准簽保守行為","createTime":"2021-02-08T07:08:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T10:13:09.000Z","uid":301533,"like":63,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"63f77d35de3b9e368a428f7e2802e49640b36219","tid":2399464,"uid":301533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:08:08.000Z","msg":"一名食物環境衞生署助理小販管理主任涉嫌在激安殿堂(Donki)盜取俗稱「飛機杯」的性玩具被捕，警誡下並認是貪心取來自己用，被控盜竊，案件今（8日）在九龍城裁判法院提堂，獲批准以1,000元簽簿守行為，並付300元訟費。<br />\n被告為李炬德（30歲），現職食環署助理小販管理主任，被控一項盜竊罪。<br />\n<br />\n警誡下認貪心偷下自己用<br />\n<br />\n案情指他在2020年12月22日晚上近9時，在尖沙咀美麗華廣場二期的激安殿堂被店員發現其形跡可疑，尾隨後發現他在貨架上取走一盒價值379.9元的性玩具震動器，並將之放到其衞衣袋內，及後拆下涉案性玩具的包裝，並用紙巾包裹包裝盒丢掉。被告在警誡下表示，「一時貪心，偷嚟自己用」。<br />\n<br />\n被告今日承認控罪，被准以1,000元自簽擔保守行為，並繳付300元訟費。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A1QvJiX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA1QvJiX.jpg&h=1d3550c3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d6ba3fc8694720a004b00c756848d3178a7ebed7","tid":2399464,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:08:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48697be646103db930d3c5831950d2a35fdbf7fd","tid":2399464,"uid":78243,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:08:49.000Z","msg":"影到個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cda60f0bb87776a4e7431d03e5c980c220f15d0","tid":2399464,"uid":244876,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T07:08:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa